    public class StartEndTimePopup
extends DialogBoxWithCloseButton
    A popup which allows a user to select start and end times. The start time is guaranteed to be earlier or in some exceptional cases, equal to, the end time. Clients should use the setTimeSelectionHandler(StartEndTimeHandler) method to set a callback for when the times have been selected
    Author:
    Guy Griffiths
